hudson.tasks.Shell.command: #!/bin/bash tmpGoDep=/tmp/rhobotGolangDependencies.tar.gz artGoDep=/artifacts/rhobotGolangDependencies.tar.gz if [ -f $artGoDep ]; then echo "Backup '$artGoDep' into Workspace '$WORKSPACE'" cp $artGoDep "art.rhobotGolangDependencies.tar.gz.$(date +"%Y-%m-%d-%H:%M")" else echo "The File '$artGoDep' Does Not Exist" fi if [ -f $tmpGoDep ]; then echo "Backup '$tmpGoDep' into Workspace '$WORKSPACE'" cp $tmpGoDep "tmp.rhobotGolangDependencies.tar.gz.$(date +"%Y-%m-%d-%H:%M")" echo "Copy '$tmpGoDep' to '$artGoDep' overwriting" \cp -f $tmpGoDep $artGoDep else echo "The File '$tmpGoDep' Does Not Exist" fi
